    "causal_summary": "The code-graph SQLite DB + sidecars + lease + readiness marker were created at the workspace-root `.opencode/.spec-kit/code-graph/database/`. The operator wants them inside the skill folder. The prior consolidation (ADR-002/004/005) justified `.spec-kit` by cross-runtime sharing, but that rationale was wrong: every runtime symlinks `.opencode/skills` to one physical dir, so a skill-local DB is equally shared.",
